data.description: It's the peaceful home you've always wanted! Come and see this 3 bedroom, 1.5 bathroom townhome with a 2 carports that will give you 1,323 sq ft of generous space to move about, all while maintaining a quaint, cozy atmosphere. Wake up each morning to your beautiful kitchen complete with granite counters, updated cabinets and stainless steel appliances, and drift off to sleep each night to the cool breeze of your newer ceiling fans. Situated in a highly desirable area, just minutes to shops and restaurants, and 10 minutes from downtown Sacramento.
